1. *Hladno* je sinoć bilo. (It was cold last night.)
2. Ona je *hladno* odgovorila. (She answered coldly.)
3. On je stavio *hladno* pivo na stol. (He put a cold beer on the table.)
4. Došla mu je *hladna* ruka. (His hand was cold.)
5. On je zakuhao *hladnu* vodu. (He boiled cold water.)
6. *Hladno* je u ovom uredu. (It's cold in this office.)
7. Oni su se *hladno* gledali. (They looked at each other coldly.)
8. Ona je osetila *hladnoću* u sobi. (She felt the coldness in the room.)